nBut what difference have these changes made to people living here?\n\nWorking in adult social care, I earn little more than the minimum wage. Like many of the people living in St Mary's, I don’t go to the cinema. And the minimum wage doesn’t buy much coffee.\n\nOur councillors need to look wider and deeper than shiny buildings.","tw":"\"hopefullannie\""},{"n":"William Hingston","p":"Conservative and Unionist Party","v":267,"r":4,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"129725"},{"n":"Lynne Christine Thompson","p":"Liberal Democrats","v":144,"r":5,"e":false,"g":"female","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"44691"},{"n":"Anthony Prince","p":"Independent","v":143,"r":6,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"existing","cf":"high","pid":"51144","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/51144/81302220-e986-4554-a996-b0176f4e169a.png","tw":"\"SupercityPrin\""}]},{"ward":"Saddleworth North","seats":1,"turnout_pct":54.48,"results_url":"https://www.oldham.gov.uk/election_results_may7_2026","candidates":[{"n":"loan Williams","p":"Reform UK","v":1752,"r":1,"e":true,"g":"male","m":"existing","cf":"high","pid":"129665","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/129665/bb0f417e-0650-43e0-85b0-af07819578e4.png"},{"n":"Michael Robert Thomas Powell","p":"Liberal Democrats","v":1289,"r":2,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"existing","cf":"high","pid":"14647","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/images/14647.png","url":"\"https://michaelpowell.mycouncillor.org.uk/\""},{"n":"Luke Bywater","p":"Conservative and Unionist Party","v":488,"r":3,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"129662","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/media/images/people/129662/90d333e5-15a7-4f99-b218-993951976213.png"},{"n":"Samuel Jacob Hollis","p":"Labour and Co-operative Party","v":432,"r":4,"e":false,"g":"male","m":"gender_guesser","cf":"high","pid":"129664","img":"https://candidates.democracyclub.org.uk/me